data.description: MOVE IN READY LIGHT AND BRIGHT!  This charming home has 3-4 bedrooms/2 full bathrooms and is waiting for you to make it yours.  Original wood flooring, neutral colors, and a flex space that may be used as a gaming room, principal bedroom, or home office.  The family room and dining room are accessible from the front entry. The galley-style kitchen is located in the heart of the residence.  Each bedroom has plenty of closet space and is a good size.  A screened porch and a storage structure are located in the backyard.  This property is located on a desirable street with mature trees. Call today to schedule your tour and experience everything this property has to offer!
